  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Anthropology              : Ethnographic survey of Native cultures in North America. Conditions arising from European colonization and their social, economic and political impact. Contemporary situation of indigenous peoples.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

